    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="J188">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Make me a picture of the sun --</l>
                    <l>So I can hang it in my room --</l>
                    <l>And make believe I'm getting warm</l>
                    <l>When others call it "Day"!</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Draw me a Robin -- on a stem --</l>
                    <l>So I am hearing him, I'll dream,</l>
                    <l>And when the Orchards stop their tune --</l>
                    <l>Put my pretense -- away --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Say if it's really -- warm at noon --</l>
                    <l>Whether it's Buttercups -- that "skim" --</l>
                    <l>Or Butterflies -- that "bloom"?</l>
                    <l>Then -- skip -- the frost -- upon the lea --</l>
                    <l>And skip the Russet -- on the tree --</l>
                    <l>Let's play those -- never come!</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
        </body>
